✨G I V E A W A Y✨

•5-night stay for 2 at Lands in Love resort located in Costa Rican Jungle 
•all meals included as well as:
•Canopy tour and Tarzan swing
•Adventure cables/zipline/ Superman 
•Canyoning 
•Whitewater rafting 

Keep reading for details on how to enter !

I just spent some of the best days of my life so far at the breathtaking
@landsinlove_tierrasenamor , a non-profit that encompasses everything I believe in.
The story of this place is amazing- 16 friends and animal lovers from Israel moved to Costa Rica together and took over an abandoned hotel to turn it into a no-kill rescue for over 1000 animals @animalloverescue . The rescue is able to save so many lives who have been abused and neglected thanks to volunteers, donations, and proceeds from the resort. (They also serve some of the best vegan food I've ever had 🥰)
Compassion, love, and connection with nature are thick in the air here and I can't thank Lands in Love enough for inviting me out to spend some time in this beautiful country.

The tourism industry was hit extremely hard over the last few years, which greatly affected the rescue's ability to bring in money. They do not EVER turn down an animal in need, and expenses are always rising. That's why I'm urging all of my friends and followers to donate and support this amazing cause. Hit the link in my bio to donate and you will also be entered to win the free stay detailed above! Every $5 donated is one entry, there is no limit to how many entries you can have, and I will pick the winner. (Note: this is the ONLY account that will contact you about winning. Watch out for scammers!!)
I will announce the winner in 2 week :) 
If you aren't able to donate, please consider tagging your friends and sharing this post to boost its reach everything helps!
#costarica #animalrescue #nonprofit #saveanimals #vegan #veganresort #compassionforall
